{"data":[{"date":"11:22 11/08","title":"Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Arsenal, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1eafp c\u00f3 sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/khong-phai-arsenal-day-moi-la-doi-bong-sap-co-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca, theo Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dembele</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/khong-phai-arsenal-day-moi-la-doi-bong-sap-co-dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/dembele-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-arsenal-184-194031.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele</span>, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a c\u00f3 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal, phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca, theo Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele co the roi Camp Nou neu Barca mua Willian\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/arsenal-tung-chieu-doc-so-huu-dembele-khien-barca-nga-ngua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p lo ng\u1ea1i Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe s\u1ebd ra \u0111i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel tin r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng PSG, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng PSG chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Dembele \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn PSG \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho b\u1ed9 ba Mbappe, Cavani v\u00e0 Neymar. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5359","checkdouble":"194246"},{"date":"10:19 11/08","title":"HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1edbi Bernabeu c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Petr Cech ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Thibaut Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Courtois l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bernabeu thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh mu\u1ed1n g\u1ea7n g\u0169i c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Courtois \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real, The Blues thu v\u1ec1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\" target=\"_blank\">Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Bernabeu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n. L\u00fd do l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi Los Blancos l\u00e0 v\u00ec gia \u0111\u00ecnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf g\u1ea7n c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1ee7a Courtois?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1edbi Bernabeu c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri\" title=\"Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-vong-1-Premier-League-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 l\u1eafm. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Real Madrid. D\u00f9 sao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, t\u00f4i ch\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Eden Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Chelsea. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 l\u1ea7n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi Kepa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Courtois hay kh\u00f4ng, HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Kepa s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng do Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Mateo Kovacic \u00f4ng chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1edbi Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5358","checkdouble":"194240"},{"date":"09:13 11/08","title":"Klopp v\u1eabn cay c\u00fa v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ramos l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1ea7n 3 th\u00e1ng sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, n\u1ed7i \u0111au v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngu\u00f4i ngoai v\u1edbi Liverpool. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ramos v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eadt v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKlopp ch\u01b0a bu\u00f4ng tha k\u1ebb th\u00f9<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f2n ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Sergio Ramos h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n, v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai ch\u1ec9 sau 30 ph\u00fat b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a qu\u00ean m\u1ed1i th\u00f9 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd kh\u00f3 nghe. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ee7 \u0111o\u1ea1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i danh hi\u1ec7u d\u00f9 b\u1ecb s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c th\u1ebf n\u00e0o ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong \u0111\u1ee3i g\u00ec \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Ramos s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu ta suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ramos v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi x\u1ea5u ch\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1\" title=\"Ramos v\u1eadt Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ramos v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi x\u1ea5u ch\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 xa khung th\u00e0nh. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p d\u00e0nh cho con c\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p m\u1ecdi th\u1ee7 \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng &ndash; c\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00f4i s\u1ebd vui l\u00f2ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00e0y sau 40 n\u0103m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i? Kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u00fang ta n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Ramos, h\u00e3y nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 &ndash; khi c\u1eadu ta \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Juan Cuadrado nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf. Real Madrid x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, ch\u1eb3ng ai nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea9n th\u1ec9u nh\u01b0 Ramos?&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ramos v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Klopp. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Ramos c\u0169ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng cho Karius, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: &quot;G\u00ec n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn Firmino c\u1ea3m l\u1ea1nh ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng?&quot;&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/thu-mon-karius-bi-roi-loan-thi-giac-sau-cu-giat-cui-cho-cua-ramos-188-187809.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/thu-mon-karius-bi-roi-loan-thi-giac-sau-cu-giat-cui-cho-cua-ramos.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/thu-mon-karius-bi-roi-loan-thi-giac-sau-cu-giat-cui-cho-cua-ramos-188-187809.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Karius b\u1ecb r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c sau c\u00fa gi\u1eadt c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Ramos</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7n ki\u1ec3m tra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe sau khi h\u1ee9ng tr\u1ecdn pha x\u1ea5u ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00ean ph\u00eda Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/lien-doan-judo-chau-au-ramos-ha-guc-salah-bang-ky-thuat-cam-188-187251.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/lien-doan-judo-chau-au-ramos-ha-guc-salah-bang-ky-thuat-cam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/lien-doan-judo-chau-au-ramos-ha-guc-salah-bang-ky-thuat-cam-188-187251.html\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Judo ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: Ramos h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Salah b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ea5m</span><br>\r\nLi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n Judo ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u1eadn ra s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf pha tranh ch\u1ea5p gi\u1eefa Ramos v\u00e0 Salah v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n th\u1ebf b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5357","checkdouble":"194241"},{"date":"11:01 11/08","title":"HLV Emery khi\u1ebfn NHM Arsenal bu\u1ed3n vui l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-khien-nhm-arsenal-buon-vui-lan-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin vui t\u1eeb Ramsey song kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Arsenal s\u1eafp gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ramsey</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aaron Ramsey\" title=\"Aaron Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Aaron Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-40-trieu-bang-chelsea-quyet-tam-mua-bang-duoc-sao-khung-arsenal-172-193778.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ramsey</span>, Real v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin vui t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i: &ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Arsenal<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ramsey, HLV Unai Emery c\u00f2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ospina bat chinh truoc Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Ospina b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ospina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Carl Jenkinson, David Ospina v\u00e0 Joel Campbell c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. C\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n hay b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a BL\u0110&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Emile Smith Rowe v\u00e0 Eddie Nketiah s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Man City trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5356","checkdouble":"194244"},{"date":"11:08 11/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eafp chia tay Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/7/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fenerbahce h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Origi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-southampton-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tien-dao-cua-liverpool-172-194142.html\" target=\"_blank\">Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton</span> theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, song c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Divock Origi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/26/Fenerbahce-muon-dua-Divock-Origi-roi-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Divock Origi mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Firmino, Sturridge v\u00e0 Solanke, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Origi, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Watford, Crystal Palace hay Wolves, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Origi t\u1edbi Fenerbahce l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n HLV Klopp c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Origi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Fenerbahce c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Liverpool v\u00e0 Origi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Origi\" title=\"Origi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/29/sao-xit-liverpool-doi-lenh-klopp-de-ra-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Origi s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Origi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec The Kop c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTTCN H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua, song nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Origi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Klopp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5355","checkdouble":"194245"},{"date":"10:38 11/08","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 \u00fd, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. \r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Paul Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaul Pogba m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng M.U, song anh \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng. S\u1ed1 6 \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho M.U ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m khi\u1ebfn Kasper Schmeichel ph\u1ea3i b\u00f3 tay. Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, san b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Ryan Babel.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a M.U, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec1u qua ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 91 l\u1ea7n, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 68 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 54 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, 6 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, 2 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, 2 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Pogba, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi Pogba, anh chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cho CLB, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: HLV Claude Puel</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, HLV Claude Puel t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: &ldquo;Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. L\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, song Leicester \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Claude Puel phat bieu ve tran MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-giai-thich-ly-do-tai-sao-leicester-that-bai-truoc-mu.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Claude Puel kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t h\u00f9ng h\u1ed3n, song Leicester c\u1ee7a Claude Puel ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a M.U. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vardy ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U. 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua (3 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 5 thua). \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 8 trong 9 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gh\u00e9 th\u0103m s\u00e2n Old Trafford (h\u00f2a 1).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Luke Shaw</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 Ashley Young v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau World Cup 2018, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Luke Shaw ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU vs Leicester </span>v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luke Shaw ghi ban dau tien cho M.U\" title=\"Luke Shaw ghi ban dau tien cho M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/luke-shaw-noi-gi-sau-khi-ghi-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luke Shaw c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. C\u1ef1u sao Southampton l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (99) v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t (67) b\u00ean ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuke Shaw c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, anh khi\u1ebfn Ricardo Pereira b\u00ean ph\u00eda Leicester kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Shaw c\u00f2n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 67 cho h\u1ecd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, Shaw x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Wes Morgan</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Wes Morgan \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00f4i sao 34 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c khi\u1ebfn Morgan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wes Morgan co mot tran dau that vong\" title=\"Wes Morgan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/morgan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wes Morgan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1984 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, anh t\u1ecf ra ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Morgan \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb Sanchez lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Harry Maguire.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Morgan \u1edf Old Trafford l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Anh ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMorgan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Leicester trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U, n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Jonny Evans.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Jose Mourinho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U, \u00f4ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1. Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester khi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a M.U m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau World Cup 2018, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 6 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n&nbsp;th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" title=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/danh-bai-leicester-mourinho-ca-ngoi-suc-manh-tap-the-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u00f9ng MU c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y, song Mourinho v\u1eabn gi\u00fap M.U c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Old Trafford v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp trung trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Jose Mourinho b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 18 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV (th\u1eafng 11, h\u00f2a 7), ri\u00eang t\u1ea1i Premier League, &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&rdquo; th\u1eafng 9 trong s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n (h\u00f2a 1).&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u1eb7n d\u00f2 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c M.U ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Alexis Sanchez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alexis Sanchez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 cho M.U qu\u1ea3 11m ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 Paul Pogba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ngo\u00e0i ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez de mat bong qua nhieu truoc Leicester\" title=\"Sanchez \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/sanchez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng Sanchez kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 ch\u1ec9 tung ra duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, Sanchez g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung v\u1edbi Rashford v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Sanchez c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 23 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Mourinho ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Sanchez ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn NHM Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: David de Gea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea MU\" title=\"De Gea MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/de-gea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Leicester, De Gea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ph\u00fat 28, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ef1c nhanh sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Maddison, t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 75 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 De Gea ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Gray.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, trong hi\u1ec7p 1 De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u thua nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n anh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018. Trong 90 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5354","checkdouble":"194247"},{"date":"08:16 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea (21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa c\u00f9ng Sarriball","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-21h00-ngay-118-nhay-mua-cung-sarriball.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Sarri. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2017/18.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nChelsea trong l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-2 t\u1ea1i si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Man City &ldquo;v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i&rdquo; k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian sa th\u1ea3i Conte, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 mua \u0111\u1eaft b\u00e1n r\u1ebb, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Chelsea \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi thu n\u1ea1p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 Kepa v\u00e0 Kovacic, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi tri\u1ec3n &ldquo;Sarriball&rdquo; &ndash; chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda m\u00e0 Napoli t\u1eebng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-vong-1-Premier-League-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, l\u00e0m quen chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1. Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 Man City c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, l\u00e0m quen l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadt may cho Sarri, khi \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Thibaut Courtois, v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u00e2n binh Jorginho &ndash; c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t may cho Sarri, khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng Huddersfield, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec The Blues \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nHuddersfield kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a David Wagner \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean &ldquo;to\u00e0n m\u1ea1ng&rdquo;. Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t cao. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Kirklees.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd thua t\u1edbi 10 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m d\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ecbch 2018, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap The Terriers tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u1edf Premier League th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 2 l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Huddersfield v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Preview Huddersfield vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1182018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV David Wagner c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Chelsea v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a The Blues, m\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft, Huddersfield &ldquo;s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u1edd xem nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c duy nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Chelsea c\u0169ng thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Burnley &ndash; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o h\u00e0ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Chelsea vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/chelsea1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea th\u1eafng Huddersfield 3-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Hudderfield kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Chelsea 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Hudderfield th\u1eafng Chelsea tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 64 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong 5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 9/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2, thua 2 trong 7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield thua 10 tr\u1eadn, ki\u1ebfm v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 &ndash; \u00edt h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 5 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8, nh\u01b0ng 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Huddersfield \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc (3-1, 1-1)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong 19 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kovacic v\u00e0 Kepa trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Courtois, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Caballero s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Sarri, v\u1edbi Luiz &ndash; Rudier l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Hazard v\u00e0 Willian b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Danny Williams, Erik D\u1ee7m v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Juninho Bacuna.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Huddersfield vs Chelsea\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Huddersfield vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Huddersfield vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1&nbsp;Huddersfield vs Chelsea: 1-2</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua-172-193858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua-172-193858.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa</span><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Top 4, HLV Sarri s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0a The Blues tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard-172-194216.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard-172-194216.html\">HLV Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Hazard</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, d\u1eadp t\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n anh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5353","checkdouble":"194230"},{"date":"08:37 11/08","title":"Pogba n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU vs Leicester</span> trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Paul-Pogba-phat-bieu-ve-MU-sau-chien-thang-truoc-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng: Anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 91 l\u1ea7n, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 68 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 54 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, 6 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, 2 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, 2 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Pogba, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" title=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/pogba-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o sau World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft tay ngay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Mourinho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cho CLB, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5352","checkdouble":"194231"},{"date":"08:49 11/08","title":"HLV Claude Puel gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao Leicester th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-giai-thich-ly-do-tai-sao-leicester-that-bai-truoc-mu.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 56 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf Old Trafford.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 2-1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a M.U, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Claude Puel \u0111\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tham v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Leicester b\u1ecb gi\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Claude-Puel-phat-bieu-ve-tran-MU-vs-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 2-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, Sanchez \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang tay m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Leicester trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 11m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, M.U ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Leicester c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh David de Gea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuke Shaw v\u1edbi c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho M.U, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Leicester d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Vardy \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThua tr\u1eadn 1-2, Leicester \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho d\u00f9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Puel ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Leicester thua tr\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU vs Leicester</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 56 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Claude Puel phat bieu ve tran MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-giai-thich-ly-do-tai-sao-leicester-that-bai-truoc-mu.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n trong hi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Leicester g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5351","checkdouble":"194233"},{"date":"08:45 11/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eabn \"ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh\" so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-van-chua-du-trinh-so-sanh-voi-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2></h2>\u00a0</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5350","checkdouble":"194234"},{"date":"08:58 11/08","title":"Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh pen v\u1edbi Sanchez","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/bo-doi-ngoi-sao-se-quyet-dinh-thanh-bai-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City \u2013 \u201c\u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d c\u1ee7a Man United, Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh penalty v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPogba g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Sanchez<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i Premier League, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc The Foxes. H\u1ecd s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Alexis Sanchez khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00f9ng tay ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, nh\u01b0ng Pogba m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Chile, nh\u1eb1m nh\u1eadn l\u1ea5y qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra. Pogba c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1eafc b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0o, h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Kasper Schmeichel tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CLB m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m penalty th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn l\u1ea5y n\u00f3. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t cho Alexis. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh penalty v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez\" title=\"Pogba thuc hien thanh cong penalty cho M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Claude-Puel-phat-bieu-ve-tran-MU-vs-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh penalty v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, t\u00f4i m\u1edbi quay l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t, phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. T\u00f4i th\u00edch nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tham gia v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u&rdquo; &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Pogba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh penalty v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t scandal nh\u01b0 Neymar &ndash; Cavani. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, Mourinho c\u0169ng trao cho Pogba chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Thong-tin-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&amp;autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-tran-mu-21-leicester-bong-dang-sieu-doi-truong-xuat-hien-172-194228.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-leicester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-tran-mu-21-leicester-bong-dang-sieu-doi-truong-xuat-hien-172-194228.html\">M.U 2-1 Leicester: B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng &ldquo;Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t v\u1edbi HLV Mourinho, Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p quan tr\u1ecdng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\">Mourinho g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: &ldquo;Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y. HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5349","checkdouble":"194235"},{"date":"23:24 10/08","title":"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/van-quyet-dai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-olympic-viet-nam-len-duong-du-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 1 trong 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1eddi ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch t\u1eeb NHM song V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Chi\u1ec1u 10/8, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 A h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ef1 A h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Van-Quyet-giai-bay-truoc-khi-cung-Olympic-Viet-Nam-len-duong-du-A-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft: \"N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec c\u1ea3 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea3. Vi\u1ec7c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea7u t\u00f4i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m vinh d\u1ef1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian qua c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch c\u1ea3. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e3y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. Anh chia s\u1ebb: \"L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn r\u00f5 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u ph\u00eda. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh, \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh, gi\u00e0nh th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14.5pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#4C4947\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5348","checkdouble":"194206"},{"date":"23:24 10/08","title":"C\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao \"v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\" d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/10/minh-vuong-noi-gi-khi-duoc-thay-park-trao-ve-vot-du-asiad-18.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD.</h2><h2>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao \"v\u00e9 v\u1edbt\"?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 1 trong s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y khi b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo g\u1ea1t ra kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 ASIAD cho anh.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao v\u00e9 v\u1edbt d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao v\u00e9 v\u1edbt d\u1ef1 ASIAD 18 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/10/Minh-Vuong-duoc-goi-bo-sung-len-tuyen-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/8, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb VFF, khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c thu d\u1ecdn h\u00e0nh trang t\u1eeb qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n bay di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb nhanh v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean\u00a0Goal.com\u00a0sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3 h\u1edfi: \"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o s\u00e1ng nay, em c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Em th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i em s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng mai 1/8. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a HAGL t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao khi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc s\u00e1t ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u00a0<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \" open=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5347","checkdouble":"194207"}]}